What is firewall-


1. Firewall software
2. network firewall

Firewall-

Ubuntu firewall you can configure using the iptables but iptable are complicated so ubuntu gives an tool called ufw.
You can manage & configure the ubuntu system firewall using ufw.


How to see firewall status?
sudo ufw status
How to see enable the firewall?
sudo ufw enable
How to see all the roles?
sudo ufw status verbose
